#

Pineapple Coconut Refresher

5 min
$3.5
80 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Gluten FreeVeganLow Calorie

Cuisine:

TropicalAmerican

Course:

DrinkAppetizer

Tags:

DrinkRefreshingTropical

Description

A refreshing tropical drink that combines the sweetness of pineapple with creamy coconut for a perfect thirst quencher!

Ingredients

  • pineapple juice: 1 cup
  • coconut water: 1 cup
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • ice cubes: 1 cup
  • mint leaves (for garnish): a few leaves
